    ('CSCI-C 212', 'INTRODUCTION TO SOFTWARE SYSTEMS', '5663', 'Class Status', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 3:55 PM–5:10 PM', 'MO 007', 'Joshua Crotts', 50, 'Lecture', 'Lecture', '4', 'MORRISON HALL', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Design of computer software systems and introduction to programming in the environment of a contemporary operating system. Topics include a modern object-oriented programming language; building and maintaining large projects; and understanding the operating system interface.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd N&M credit'], NULL),
